2. Nf3 {[%csl Re5]} { Developing the knight with tempi, hitting the e5-pawn, is our best move against the Open Games. } Nc6 { This is their most popular choice at all levels. Every now and then we might face a different defence of the pawn. Let's check them briefly. } 
3. Nc3 Nf6 
