17. exd5 Nb4? ( { Black should have played } 17...Nd4 18.c3 Ndf5 19.Ne2 b5 20.O-O-O b4 21.Be4 { and White is better, but it's a game. } ) 
18. a3 Nbxd5?? ( { Black's last chance to avoid losing a piece was } 18...Na6 { . } ) 
