12. a4! {[%cal Gb2b4,Gb4b5][%csl Rc8]} { The start of a strong queenside offensive. White is scoring nearly 80% with this plan in my grand master games database. White won in twenty-two moves in the game between Moreno Carnero, J and Peixoto, A Loures 1998 [/variation/41248783/#/12/w]. This game can be found in the model games section. } *

