3. e5 { By advancing our pawn, we increase our space advantage. } Bf5 { The knight on c6 puts more pressure in the center and also reinforces the pawn break ... f7-f6. However, it does impede the typical break ...c5. All in all, a double-edged option. } 
4. c3 e6 
